## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the scope of the research. The findings are based on a selection of studies and articles, which may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. Additionally, the complexity of human behavior means that the pursuit of status can vary significantly across different cultures and individual experiences. Further research could explore these variations in greater detail.